%% Diagram: Upload-side processing pipeline
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    UPLOAD[Upload complete] --> VALIDATE[Validate<br/>format, size, duration]
    VALIDATE --> EXTRACT[Probe metadata<br/>resolution, codec, FPS, audio tracks]
    EXTRACT --> THUMB[Generate thumbnails<br/>frames + sprite sheet]
    EXTRACT --> SEGMENT[Segment + GOP align<br/>2-4s chunks at IDR boundaries]
    SEGMENT --> ANALYZE[Per-shot analysis<br/>scene change, complexity]
    ANALYZE --> QUEUE[Fan out transcode jobs<br/>chunks x codecs x rungs]
    THUMB --> READY[Mark video discoverable]
    QUEUE --> READY
